### =========================================================
### Product Mint API
### Scope: SCOPE_BRAND_MINT
### =========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@brandAccessToken = 79bcd28c-5205-4bd8-9fb1-05ed1913e579
@tenantId = 4be926c6-39ce-4622-8ca4-86149abd2894

### 1) Minted (Genesis)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/tenants/{{tenantId}}/minted
Authorization: Bearer {{brandAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "serialNumber": "SN-20260305-0001",
  "modelId": "MODEL-001",
  "modelName": "Cyber Sneaker V1",
  "manufacturedAt": "2026-03-05T00:00:00Z",
  "productionBatch": "BATCH-01",
  "factoryCode": "F-KR-01",
  "componentRootHash": "aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa"
}

### 2) List Minted Passports
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/tenants/{{tenantId}}/minted
Authorization: Bearer {{brandAccessToken}}
